{"type": "article", "id": 21349, "title": "母子闹钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-27T07:30:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154126Suvlyr7LhQkwObHd.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙设计师 Héctor Serrano 在巴黎家博会上带来了这款闹钟的设计，在普通的长方体的闹钟上有一个缩小版，是专门用来定时的。按下去后恢复成普通的长方体，意味着定时取消。闹钟背后的加减号是用来设定时间的，非常形象。这款闹钟是为法国商务礼品公司 Lexon 设计的，目前还没有出售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150914sEN1uzK7f9aqpLck.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150915xSnNuEBVJkQ9pCRH.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"676\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150916RtkwdX8PZgBGbT7j.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"666\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150916vMIGbK0RT83WVmrd.jpg\" width=\"816\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66789216\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}